metadata.name: Morphology #39
metadata.description: Abstract animated glitchy patterns form and morph. A diverse range of shapes are created from the algorithm. Sometimes fractal like patterns occur in the piece. The animation can often look noisy and chaotic however patterns emerge from the chaos. sometimes long streaks of pixels form all over the canvas reminiscent of a cybernetic pollock

metadata.name: Wide Vortex #3
metadata.description:
Wide Vortex of warped lines. Made in P5.js
Features: One of 19 palettes.
Black background or 1 of 5 rare backgrounds (White, Deep Gray, Deep Blue, Deep Green, Deep Red)
The chance of more or less tightly packed vortex.
Best seen in full-screen mode where you can press s to save. 
Also made to look awesome on phone or small screen sizes. 

Made by P1xelboy :
@p1x3lboy Jan 2022
